Paccayānulomapaccanīya
Vippayuttaduka
Tika
617Vippayuttapaccayā hetupaccayā naārammaṇe pañca, naadhipatiyā sattarasa, naanantare pañca, nasamanantare pañca, naaññamaññe pañca, naupanissaye pañca, napurejāte pañca, napacchājāte sattarasa, naāsevane sattarasa, nakamme satta, navipāke sattarasa, nasampayutte pañca, nonatthiyā pañca, novigate pañca.
